recipe-iridium-matrix-name = iridium matrix synthesis (×5)
recipe-iridium-matrix-description = Compress diamond, fissile uranium, bluespace and plasma into five units of stabilized isotopic lattice. First stage of iridite metallurgy.

recipe-cryo-binder-name = cryo binder synthesis (×5)
recipe-cryo-binder-description = Mix plastitanium, lithium, silver and pyrogel into five units of cryogenic binding agent. Second stage of iridite metallurgy.

recipe-iridite-smelting-name = iridite smelting (×5)
recipe-iridite-smelting-description = Fuse iridium matrix and cryo binder with steel, gold and copper under extreme centrifuge pressure. Produces five iridite sheets per batch.

drake-centrifuge-iridium-matrix-name = Drake iridium matrix synthesis (×5)
drake-centrifuge-iridium-matrix-desc = An optimized Drake process for iridium matrix with reduced material costs.
drake-centrifuge-cryo-binder-name = Drake cryo binder synthesis (×5)
drake-centrifuge-cryo-binder-desc = An optimized Drake process for cryo binder with reduced material costs.
drake-centrifuge-iridite-name = Drake iridite smelting (×5)
drake-centrifuge-iridite-desc = An optimized Drake process for iridite smelting with reduced material costs and faster cycle time. Produces five sheets per batch.
